title.narrative: Communication Materials and Supplies - Miscellaneous Supplies and Materials (NOC) (A, B, C) (ITA) (INS) (FAS). FY-2014 Credit Card. Administrative Supplies - Office Supplies (A, B, C) (ITA) (INS)

description.narrative: Non-Proliferation. INM-EOP[Covers the cost of supply items not otherwise classified. Includes petty cash purchases as distinguished from specific purpose vouchers.]. INM-EOP[Covers the cost of typewriters, adding machines, calculators, copying, and other machines used in an office. This excludes machines used in the Central Reproduction Plant and for telegram processing.]. INM-EOP[Covers rental costs of toll-free (WATS) telephone lines under Other Communications.]. GENERAL SERVICES[Covers the costs of office supplies, stationary, forms, paper, other supplies, and minor equipment items.]. AMBASSADORS-AT-LARGE[Covers the furnishing of an office including furniture and furnishings. Furniture includes desks, chairs, tables, bookcases, file cabinets, clothes racks, etc. It excludes movable appliances such as window-type air conditioners, water coolers, and portable heaters. Furnishings include rugs, draperies, window shades, pictures, mirrors, lamps, etc.]
